#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:37
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:46
msgid "What is Chatea-Conecta?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:62
msgid ""
"Chatea-Conecta is a free and anonymous chat platform that allows users to "
"connect with others worldwide in real-time. No login or registration is "
"required to join the conversation."
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:67
msgid "How do I start chatting?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:83
msgid ""
"Simply go to the homepage, enter a username of your choice in the input "
"field, and click 'Start Chatting'. You'll instantly join a global chat room "
"with other users."
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:88
msgid "Is Chatea-Conecta really anonymous?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:104
msgid ""
"Yes! You don't need to provide any personal information to use the platform. "
"However, avoid sharing sensitive details in the chat for your own safety."
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:109
msgid "Is there a mobile version of Chatea-Conecta?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:125
msgid ""
"Yes, Chatea-Conecta is fully responsive and works seamlessly on mobile, "
"tablet, and desktop devices. You can enjoy chatting on the go!"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:130
msgid "Can I report inappropriate behavior in the chat?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:146
msgid ""
"Yes. If you encounter inappropriate content, use the 'Report' button in the "
"chat interface. This helps us maintain a safe and welcoming environment for "
"all users."
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:151
msgid "Does Chatea-Conecta store my chat messages?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:167
msgid ""
"No, Chatea-Conecta does not store chat messages. All conversations are real-"
"time and ephemeral, ensuring your privacy."
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:172
msgid "How is Chatea-Conecta secure?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:188
msgid ""
"We use HTTPS to encrypt all communication between your device and our "
"servers. This ensures a safe and secure chat experience."
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:193
msgid "Why do I see promotional messages in the chat?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:209
msgid ""
"We monetize the platform by including occasional promotional messages sent "
"by bots. These messages are marked as 'Promotions' to distinguish them from "
"real users."
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:214
msgid "Can I block promotional messages?"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/faq.html:230
msgid ""
"At this time, promotional messages cannot be blocked, but we strive to keep "
"them minimal and non-intrusive."
msgstr ""

