#: chat_connect/templates/pages/privacy.html:48
msgid "Information We Collect"
msgstr ""

#: chat_connect/templates/pages/privacy.html:49
msgid ""
"We do not collect or store any personal information. The only information we "
"process is the username you create upon accessing our app. This username can "
"be any set of characters of your choice and is not linked to your personal "
"identity."
